# Google Places API - needed for live Google reviews on the website
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit real values to the repo! This is a PUBLIC repository.
#     Use GitHub Secrets for production (see below).
#
# === LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ===
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in the values below
# 3. .env is in .gitignore and will NOT be committed
#
# === PRODUCTION (GitHub Pages) ===
# Secrets are injected via GitHub Actions during build.
# To set them up:
# 1. Go to your repo → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions
# 2. Add these repository secrets:
#    - GOOGLE_API_KEY
#    - GOOGLE_PLACE_ID
#
# === HOW TO GET THE VALUES ===
#
# API Key:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Enable "Places API"
# 3. Create an API key under APIs & Services > Credentials
# 4. (Recommended) Restrict the key to "Places API" only
#
# Place ID:
# 1. Go to https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/web-service/place-id
# 2. Search "Awesome Works AI"
# 3. Copy the Place ID

GOOGLE_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=
